OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FA headteacher has turned to technology
OL,8,Fto try and stop students skipping
OL,9,Fclass to vape in the toilets.
OL,11,FTony McCabe says pupils as young as 11
OL,12,Fare starting at his secondary school,
OL,13,FSt Joseph's RC High School in Horwich,
OL,14,Fin Greater Manchester, addicted to
OL,15,Fvapes.
OL,17,FMr McCabe said: "The vape sensors were
OL,18,Ffitted into every single toilet
OL,19,Fcubicle.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
