OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FThe school decided to install them
OL,8,Fafter several students needed hospital
OL,9,Ftreatment after using contaminated
OL,10,Fvapes - including one who stopped
OL,11,Fbreathing for a period of time.
OL,13,FPupils are not punished if they are
OL,14,Ffound with a vape and are instead
OL,15,Fgiven help to beat their addiction, Mr
OL,16,FMcCabe said.
OL,18,FThe school's focus is on student
OL,19,Fsafety and educating both children and
OL,20,Fparents about the risks of vaping.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
