OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FBut despite this, some children still
OL,8,Ftry and hid their vapes in their
OL,9,Fshoes, hair and clothing.
OL,11,FThe number of children who vape has
OL,12,Ftripled over the past three years,
OL,13,Ffigures from the Department of Health
OL,14,Fand Social Care show - with around 9%
OL,15,Fof 11 to 15 years olds now vaping.
OL,17,FThe North West has the highest number
OL,18,Fof teenagers who vape, a survey from
OL,19,FGo Smoke Free also found.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
