OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FIn September Greater Manchester Police
OL,8,Fseized a haul of illicit and
OL,9,Fcounterfeit vapes believed to be worth
OL,10,Faround #1 million, hidden behind a
OL,11,Fsecret door in a vape shop in Salford.
OL,13,FHowever police admit it is an ongoing
OL,14,Fbattle to keep potentially harmful
OL,15,Fproducts off the streets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
