OL,3,CThe school using sensors and metal
OL,4,Cdetectors to protect their pupils from
OL,5,Cvapes
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Rick
OL,8,FThompson from Greater Manchester
OL,9,FPolice said: "We had our first case of
OL,10,Fa child being hospitalised (because of
OL,11,Fa contaminated vape) in 2019 and as a
OL,12,Fresult we have used Operation Mandrake
OL,13,Fwhich allows us to test substances
OL,14,Fafterwards and put alerts out.
OL,16,F"To give you some idea of the scale of
OL,17,Fit - in 2021 the UK Border Agency
OL,18,Fseized around 4,500 illegal vapes.
OL,20,F"In 2023 that was over four and a half
OL,21,Fmillion - so it's a really big issue."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
